{"tid":192774,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"whatsapp表白定面對面表白","createTime":"2017-04-08T19:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T02:06:32.000Z","uid":44704,"like":4,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e44511024da5743961694ce817f3030ccec635f8","tid":192774,"uid":44704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T19:44:58.000Z","msg":"正皮：whatsapp<br />\n負皮：面對面<br />\n<br />\n兩樣都試過，其實緊張感兩個都冇乜唔同<br />\nWhatsapp成日俾人話冇誠意<br />\n但係面對面又可能令條女一時反應唔切"},{"pid":"cb5f2018677fb5e8a47a3811413468de37762c43","tid":192774,"uid":102983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T19:51:52.000Z","msg":"梗係唔表白"},{"pid":"48639ec773a7c53f34973e22647d9625b32b4e29","tid":192774,"uid":67141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T19:56:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梗係唔表白</blockquote><br />\n正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59441cea9e3e60ef793977864386a16e3e50904f","tid":192774,"uid":88813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T20:00:33.000Z","msg":"十拿九穩就當面啦<br />\n<br />\n唔肯定/ 但求表完白等自己死心就whatsapp 啦"},{"pid":"5980578ff87743ca25d33ef050fed9363baea246","tid":192774,"uid":44704,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T20:03:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梗係唔表白</blockquote><br />\n其實都係 表白好似只係一個儀式咁<br />\n不過老土啲講句 拖完手錫完其實都唔代表一齊<br />\n始終表完白會確實到個關係<br />\n無論係成功定失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdca6c883d69b26f0fc1510e3d56d9ff1a73dd9a","tid":192774,"uid":44704,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T20:05:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十拿九穩就當面啦<br />\n<br />\n唔肯定/ 但求表完白等自己死心就whatsapp 啦</blockquote><br />\n等自己死心既表白不如唔好表<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n認同你，十拿九穩就面對面，唔肯定就whatsapp<br />\n但可能靠現場氣氛同鋪排，唔肯定都可能變肯定"},{"pid":"c69fc4d6a9471de9dc922edcd30e6defe970b941","tid":192774,"uid":30929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T20:07:24.000Z","msg":"要一齊使閪表白咩 <br />\n拖/錫到咪表白成功囉"},{"pid":"c0a4f3f9d605589bb8e7069efe2c00ed8b524ddf","tid":192774,"uid":72906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T20:07:32.000Z","msg":"佢唔鍾意你點表白都冇用"},{"pid":"73bc1ebf8253de4fc0a954fb22ce89ef5006f6df","tid":192774,"uid":25496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T20:10:30.000Z","msg":"表白既作用係用黎確定關係 而唔係用黎搏 好老定既話點表都無問題<br />\n<br />\n個人觀感 兩樣都被試過 當面表係好有勇氣 但好考反應 一個唔覺意俾人拒絕要識執生"},{"pid":"d85435ab8b9cb0c33a63c30c50e6d8383baee201","tid":192774,"uid":44704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T20:30:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要一齊使閪表白咩 <br />\n拖/錫到咪表白成功囉</blockquote><br />\n唔一定拖/錫到就得米<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251a7c6ab9dfb976f839e7ab01a751ecbeb14e1d","tid":192774,"uid":44704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T20:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢唔鍾意你點表白都冇用</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你唔知佢鍾唔鍾意你呢？點抉擇"},{"pid":"d809e6cc1b1e5ee5e40ccdfc3ad8c5de71f9889c","tid":192774,"uid":44704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T20:32:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>表白既作用係用黎確定關係 而唔係用黎搏 好老定既話點表都無問題<br />\n<br />\n個人觀感 兩樣都被試過 當面表係好有勇氣 但好考反應 一個唔覺意俾人拒絕要識執生</blockquote><br />\n如果係知道對你有好感但唔老定？<br />\n如果當面被拒絕又可以點應對"},{"pid":"2a27d19b3cdff5b535480c8e518130a7ff5701c2","tid":192774,"uid":44704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T02:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}